description:
** Most popular and copied stopwatch app on WebOS, oh yes we said copied into other apps. Winner of Palm Hot apps. \n

*******Ability to keep the screen on while open, Ability to switch to countdown timer, and a preference for having the lap appear at the top of the list! If you dont have countdown install it will open the catalog for you. ***********This is a simple timer with lap/split time. If you have the timer running while in the background a notification will be shown each minute. This application supports both landscape and portrait views.

If you have an suggestions please let us know.&nbsp;
